|~ Root qlang catalog — pulls in every operand family plus shared
   runtime-invariant tag-bindings and the value-class constructors
   (::conduit / ::qlang / ::json). The actual catalog content lives
   in lib/qlang/operand/<family>.qlang, lib/qlang/runtime-invariants.qlang,
   and lib/qlang/tag.qlang. Each family file declares its operands
   and their per-site error tags inline; runtime-invariants carries
   shared/cross-family errors plus the parser / codec / dispatch
   invariant tags.

   Type vocabulary (flat keywords) used in :subject / :returns /
   :modifiers across every family:
     :number :string :boolean :keyword :null :any
     :vec :map :set
     :predicateLambda :keyLambda :comparatorLambda
     :pipeline (captured sub-pipeline, lazy) ~|

use([:qlang/runtime-invariants
     :qlang/tag
     :qlang/operand/arith
     :qlang/operand/vec
     :qlang/operand/container
     :qlang/operand/setOp
     :qlang/operand/mapOp
     :qlang/operand/string
     :qlang/operand/comparator
     :qlang/operand/predicate
     :qlang/operand/typeClassifier
     :qlang/operand/typeConversion
     :qlang/operand/control
     :qlang/operand/format
     :qlang/operand/reflective
     :qlang/operand/error
     :qlang/operand/codeAsData
     :qlang/operand/axis])
